{"text_id":13768,"tokens":["The"," Mongols","'"," military"," campaigns"," are"," often"," portrayed"," as"," a"," relentless"," and"," unstoppable"," force",","," sweeping"," across"," large"," areas"," and"," leaving"," destruction"," in"," their"," wake","."," However",","," a"," closer"," examination"," of"," their"," military"," strategies"," and"," tactics"," reveals"," several"," inherent"," weaknesses"," that"," limited"," their"," effectiveness"," in"," certain"," contexts","."," Firstly",","," the"," Mongols"," relied"," heavily"," on"," nomadic"," warfare",","," which"," was"," effective"," in"," their"," early"," campaigns"," against"," other"," nomadic"," tribes","."," However",","," this"," approach"," became"," less"," effective"," against"," settled"," populations"," with"," fortified"," cities"," and"," armies"," that"," employed"," siege"," warfare",".","\n\n","Secondly",","," the"," Mongols","'"," reliance"," on"," mobility"," and"," speed"," meant"," that"," they"," were"," vulnerable"," to"," amb","ushes"," and"," surprise"," attacks"," from"," opponents"," who"," were"," familiar"," with"," the"," terrain","."," The"," Mongols","'"," extensive"," use"," of"," cavalry"," also"," made"," them"," vulnerable"," to"," attacks"," by"," infantry"," forces"," that"," were"," equipped"," with"," projectile"," weapons",","," such"," as"," catap","ults"," and"," cannons",".","\n\n","Third","ly",","," the"," Mongols","'"," organizational"," structure"," was"," based"," on"," a"," tribal"," system",","," which"," was"," effective"," for"," mobili","zing"," large"," numbers"," of"," warriors"," over"," short"," distances","."," However",","," this"," system"," became"," less"," effective"," in"," more"," complex"," and"," hierarchical"," societies",","," such"," as"," those"," found"," in"," Europe"," and"," China",".","\n\n","Furthermore",","," the"," Mongols","'"," military"," campaigns"," were"," often"," driven"," by"," a"," desire"," for"," booty"," and"," spoils",","," rather"," than"," ideological"," or"," strategic"," goals","."," This"," led"," to"," a"," lack"," of"," discipline"," and"," strategic"," direction"," in"," their"," military"," operations",","," as"," individual"," warriors"," and"," commanders"," pursued"," their"," own"," interests"," rather"," than"," working"," towards"," a"," unified"," goal",".","\n\n","In"," addition",","," the"," Mongols","'"," military"," strategies"," were"," often"," reactive"," rather"," than"," proactive",","," responding"," to"," the"," actions"," of"," their"," enemies"," rather"," than"," taking"," the"," initiative"," themselves","."," This"," reactive"," approach"," often"," led"," to"," a"," piece","meal"," and"," disorganized"," response"," to"," enemy"," movements",","," rather"," than"," a"," coordinated"," and"," decisive"," strike",".","\n\n","Finally",","," the"," Mongols","'"," military"," campaigns"," were"," heavily"," reliant"," on"," the"," skills"," and"," abilities"," of"," individual"," warriors",","," rather"," than"," relying"," on"," complex"," logistical"," systems"," and"," military"," infrastructure","."," While"," this"," allowed"," them"," to"," maintain"," a"," high"," level"," of"," battlefield"," effectiveness",","," it"," also"," meant"," that"," they"," were"," vulnerable"," to"," losing"," key"," leaders"," and"," warriors",","," which"," could"," disrupt"," their"," military"," operations",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," while"," the"," Mongols"," were"," a"," highly"," effective"," and"," feared"," military"," force",","," they"," were"," not"," the"," unstoppable"," force"," that"," they"," are"," often"," portrayed"," as","."," They"," had"," several"," inherent"," weaknesses"," that"," limited"," their"," effectiveness"," in"," certain"," contexts",","," including"," their"," reliance"," on"," nomadic"," warfare",","," vulnerability"," to"," amb","ushes"," and"," siege"," warfare",","," and"," lack"," of"," discipline"," and"," strategic"," direction","."],"sub_source":"reddit","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}